cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper deals with multi-person tracking, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces a novel local pairwise feature based on deep matching, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on the MOT16 benchmark, which is related to multimedia analysis, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible sub-category as well.
